content: न्यंच् {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> {@--1@} To go down, bend down; <ls>Māl. 5. 22.</ls> {@--2@} To incline. {@--3@} To diminish, pass away; न्यंचति वयसि प्रथमे <ls>Bv. 2. 47.</ls>

न्यंच् {%<ab>a.</ab>%} (नीची|{%<ab>f.</ab>%}) {@--1@} Going or turned downwards, turned or bent down. {@--2@} Lying on the face. {@--3@} Low, contemptible, base, mean, vile; <ls>Śi. 15. 21</ls> (where it also means निम्न or downward). {@--4@} Slow, lazy. {@--5@} Whole, entire.
